@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 1) Registrar usuario (copie verificationTokenForDev da resposta)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Ana Souza",
  "email": "ana@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaForte@2026"
}

### 2) Verificar email em modo dev (cole token retornado no passo 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "token": "COLE_AQUI_O_VERIFICATION_TOKEN"
}

### 3) Solicitar recuperacao de senha (dev retorna resetTokenForDev)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "ana@example.com"
}

### 4) Redefinir senha em modo dev (cole token retornado no passo 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "token": "COLE_AQUI_O_RESET_TOKEN",
  "password": "NovaSenhaForte@2026"
}

### 5) Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "ana@example.com",
  "password": "NovaSenhaForte@2026"
}

### 6) Criar primeiro lar (free: max 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/households
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer COLE_AQUI_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Lar da Ana"
}

### 7) Obter perfil + limites de plano + onboarding
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer COLE_AQUI_ACCESS_TOKEN
